color of creamed coffee and looked like a cross between a Fedora
and a Homburg, with a wide ribbed band, a rakish curl in the brim
and an uncreased oval crown as smooth and soft as a nesting dove. I
instantly knew that this splendid felt hat was perfect for Charley
Payday. (Watts, Cox News Service) MOVED MONDAY.
