   YOUNG-COLUMN _ WACO, Texas _ More and more families we know are
just like us, with one or more no-meat eaters. Commonly it is the
young people swearing it off and parents figuring out they don't
need it either. Often, adults who get accustomed to a low-fat diet
come to realize they have gone neo-vegetarian. (Young, Waco
Tribune-Herald) MOVED
</P>
