furniture is back with a vengeance. Furniture designers are
creating metal works in everything imaginable _ from tables to
chairs, to bed frames. This is the season of the silver tones:
steel, aluminum, pewter and zinc and furniture designers are doing
more as the demand increases. (Flanders, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution.) WITH PHOTOS.
