sell, a new report to Security Council says. Kofi Annan, the
secretary-general, also looks at the issue of Iraqi suffering under
the U.N. sanctions. By Barbara Crossette.
</P>
<P>
   LEBANON-ISRAEL (Dateline to kum) _ Israeli jets attack overnight
and this morning in their heaviest attacks since a big strike on
Feb. 8. Targets are hit less than a mile from Syrian border. By
John F. Burns.
</P>
<P>
   With map.
</P>
