</P>
<P>
   The Boston Architectural Center will sponsor a trip to northern
Spain in May. On Thursday at 7:30 p.m. the center, at 320 Newbury
St., will hold a slide/lecture on the trip.
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Snowmobile tours &QL; 
 &QL;
