<P>
   Snowmobile resorts in Maine are planning on grooming their
trails and offering vacation packages through the first weekend in
April. Base depths on trails range from 1 1/2 to 2 1/2 feet. For
information, call 877-275-3363 or visit www.sledme.com. All that
snow promises a good spring runoff for the white-water rafting
season that begins May 1. &QL; 
