   For a touch of St. Patrick's Day commentary, read how they
celebrate in Chicago (HINT: The river is green, the sweet rolls are
green, the beer is green...). ``PULEEEEEASE, DON'T SWIM in the
GREEN-TINTED RIVER'' by Richard Roeper, slugged:
BC-ST-PATRICKS-DAY-CHICAGO-STYLE, moved in the ``k'' commentary and
``a'' general news categories.''
