visiting the great pyramids and the tombs of the pharaohs, but only
as a tourist. Instead, he was lucky enough to go as an amateur
archeologist and helped to rediscover the greatest tomb since King
Tut's. By BARBARA YOST. Story will move in the ``L'' category. 
 
