<TEXT>
<P>
   Here are the business news stories the Los Angeles Daily News
plans to move for use by NYTimes News Service clients, AMs and PMs
of Wednesday, March 15 and thereafter. The stories will carry the
``f'' financial news category code unless otherwise noted. For
questions about stories, please contact Stewart Slavin at the Daily
News at (818) 713-3701.
</P>
<P>
   TOON-TOWN (Burbank, Calif.) _ Burbank will further cement its
reputation as 'toon city with the opening of a new Cartoon Network
production center by early June. By Marla Matzer Rose.
</P>
</TEXT>
