<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-03-14 20:27 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6806 &Cx1f; ttj-z
u w BC-CLINTON-ASIA-HNS &LR;      03-14 0756
