search engine sent an Internet surfer the insurer's way.
</P>
<P>
   Now comes one of those twists that seems blindingly obvious once
it's pointed out.
</P>
<P>
   Derick Bulkley, CEO of SeriousCollector.com, a Web site for,
yes, serious collectors (of coins, stamps, and much more), has
